Cypress on-call summary for 9/23-27
• It was hard for me to keep on top of everything because of other fires that popped up :sweat_smile:
• The main issues that I noticed were due to turning on Community on Metronome (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CSY11CK7T/p1727372102301369), and luckily they have largely been fixed
• I saw one last test that is still failing from Community on Metronome and blocking CI, so I have a fix here (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/63211)
• I saw a lot of flakey tests. Among them:
    ◦ workspace-settings.spec.ts
    ◦ context-switching.spec.ts
    ◦ aihub-redigitization.spec.ts
    ◦ (Probably more, but these are the ones that I saw today)
